flavor_text_entries.gold:
It makes a nest to
suit its long and
skinny body. The nest is impossible
for other POKéMON
to enter.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
There is no tell­
ing where the tail
begins. Despite its short legs, it
is quick at hunt­
ing RATTATA.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
It lives in narrow
burrows that fit
its slim body. The deeper the nests
go, the more maze­
like they become.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
FURRET has a very slim build.
When under attack, it can slickly squirm
through narrow spaces and get away. In spite of its short limbs, this
POKéMON is very nimble and fleet.
